                        "displayName": "Olivier Riffaud",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I've just done true REST controllers with ZF, by rewriting Zend_Controller_Request_Http like that :\r\n{code:title=Zend_Controller_Request_Http|borderStyle=solid}\r\nclass Olivier_Controller_Request_Http extends Zend_Controller_Request_Http\r\n{\r\n    public function __construct($uri = null)\r\n    {\r\n        if($this->isPut() || $this->isDelete()){\r\n            parse_str(file_get_contents('php:\/\/input'), $vars);\r\n            $this->setParams($vars);\r\n        }\r\n        parent::__construct($uri);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n{code}\r\nAnd in Zend_Rest_Route, i removed \r\n{code:php}\r\nunset($params[$this->_actionKey]);\r\n{code}\r\nBut i do PUT and DELETE HTTP request by using a Jquery bypass :\r\n{code:javascript}\r\n$.put('\/myController\/format\/html', function(data){});\r\n{code}",
